<text><body>
<lb n="0098a05"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0098a06"/>
<lb n="0098a07"/><head type="no">No. 1220</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0098a08"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0098001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】寬治四年寫仁和寺藏本，【乙】東寺三密藏古寫本</note>金剛藥叉瞋怒<note n="0098002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕－【甲】</note><app n="0098002"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>息災大威神驗
<lb n="0098a09"/>念誦儀軌</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0098a10"/>
<lb n="0098a11"/><byline type="Translator">南天竺三藏金剛智奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0098a12"/><p>爾時金剛手虛空庫菩薩摩訶薩。觀察天宮諸
<lb n="0098a13"/>大菩薩天龍等八部。而從座起偏袒<note n="0098003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝一【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098003"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app>肩。白
<lb n="0098a14"/>釋迦牟尼佛言。乃往古昔無量俱胝大劫。為
<lb n="0098a15"/>求法故。流轉<note n="0098004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔器〕－【甲】</note><app n="0098004"><lem>器</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>世間。多有波旬王<note n="0098005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等令我＝世間不令我進【甲】</note><app n="0098005"><lem>等令我</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">世間不令我進</rdg></app>
<lb n="0098a16"/><note n="0098006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多退＝進退多【乙】</note><app n="0098006"><lem>多退</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">進退多</rdg></app>佛法。唯願薄伽梵。聽示現權身說大威
<lb n="0098a17"/>神驗真言。<note n="0098007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛言〕－【甲】</note><app n="0098007"><lem>佛言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>欲現何權身。答<note n="0098008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰願＝白佛言【甲】</note><app n="0098008"><lem>曰願</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">白佛言</rdg></app>現大
<lb n="0098a18"/>聖藥叉金剛形。過去佛已現。現在佛今現。未
<lb n="0098a19"/>來佛當現。我今非過去非現在非未來。現我
<lb n="0098a20"/><note n="0098009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自心＝息災【甲】</note><app n="0098009"><lem>自心</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">息災</rdg></app>三昧忿怒。而守護佛法愍念有情。佛言
<lb n="0098a21"/>善<note n="0098010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哉＋（善哉）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098010"><lem>哉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">哉善哉</rdg></app>大聖欲護持佛法愍念有情。仁者善可
<lb n="0098a22"/>現權說大靈驗真言。我與<note n="0098011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仁＋（者）【乙】</note><app n="0098011"><lem>仁</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">仁者</rdg></app>加持護念。俱共
<lb n="0098a23"/>說真言慈護持者。即時未起座。現三面六臂
<lb n="0098a24"/>大威忿怒<note n="0098012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098012"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>毒形。以七珍瓔珞莊身。其身長
<lb n="0098a25"/>大無量遍身火焰燃。<note n="0098013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＋（盛）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0098013"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">如盛</rdg></app>劫焰&CB00195;威猛。顧視四
<lb n="0098a26"/>方如獸王<note n="0098014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔象〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098014"><lem>象</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>勇猛。誦真言先<note n="0098015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持行＝行持【甲】</note><app n="0098015"><lem>持行</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">行持</rdg></app>者。捧止
<lb n="0098a27"/>羽為鈴拳當乳上。以觀羽作劍<note n="0098016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縛＝&CB00085;【甲】＊</note><app n="0098016"><lem>縛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;</rdg></app>置膝上。以
<lb n="0098a28"/>止羽共第一噁字反拳縮引。共第二&CB00680;噁返
<lb n="0098a29"/>觀羽。<note n="0098017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔羽〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098017"><lem>羽</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>即二手如鳳威粕米勢。共第三噁下
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1220.0098b" n="0098b"/>
<lb n="0098b01"/>止上觀拍節出聲。共第四感<note n="0098018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引字甲乙兩本作細註</note><note n="0098018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（引）本文＝（引）細註【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098018"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>二羽磨轉。共
<lb n="0098b02"/><note n="0098019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（第）＋五【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098019"><lem>五</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">第五</rdg></app>發吒互止觀上下三返以拳纏身。置頂左
<lb n="0098b03"/>三轉成<note n="0098020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辟＝臂【甲】</note><app n="0098020"><lem>辟</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">臂</rdg></app>除。右三轉成結界。後以印各押四
<lb n="0098b04"/><note n="0098021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＝令&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0098021"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">令</rdg></app>。瞋目怒口。甚怖畏體誦<note n="0098022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔明〕－【乙】</note><app n="0098022"><lem>明</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0098b05"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三滿多沒馱<note n="0098023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">南＝喃【甲】＊</note><app n="0098023"><lem>南</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">喃</rdg></app><note place="inline">引一</note>阿&CB00155;迦<note place="inline">引</note>也<note place="inline">二</note>尾曩
<lb n="0098b06"/><note place="inline">引</note>也<note place="inline">三</note>噁<note place="inline">入四</note>毘只迦<note place="inline">引</note>也<app type="＊" source="0098016"><lem>縛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00085;</rdg></app>日羅菴<note place="inline">平引五</note>設咄
<lb n="0098b07"/>嚧<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00680;噁<note place="inline">引六</note>達磨薩<note n="0098024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】</note><app n="0098024"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>吒迦爾<note place="inline">若以反</note>尾
<lb n="0098b08"/>伽哩<note n="0098025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚀＝寧【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0098025"><lem>嚀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">寧</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note><note n="0098026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔尾〕－【甲】</note><app n="0098026"><lem>尾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>伽哩<app type="＊" source="0098025"><lem>嚀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">寧</rdg></app><note place="inline">引七</note>設咄嚧<note n="0098027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098027"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>吽<note place="inline">引
<lb n="0098b09"/>平</note>噁<note place="inline">入八</note>訖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>訖哩<note place="inline">二合<note n="0098028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔九〕－【甲】</note><app n="0098028"><lem>九</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>伽&CB00576;<note n="0098029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八〕－【甲】</note><app n="0098029"><lem><note place="inline">八</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>伽&CB00576;<note place="inline"><note n="0098030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入引九＝八【甲】</note><app n="0098030"><lem>入引九</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">八</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0098b10"/>伽伽&CB00576;<note n="0098031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引十感入十一＝引九感入十【甲】</note><app n="0098031"><lem><note place="inline">引十</note>感<note place="inline">入十一</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">引九感入十</note></rdg></app>嗚<note n="0098032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祖＝&CB03310;【甲】</note><app n="0098032"><lem>祖</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB03310;</rdg></app><note place="inline">主於反</note>摩羅&CB00576;<note place="inline">引</note>設<note n="0098033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咄＋（&CB03320;）【甲】</note><app n="0098033"><lem>咄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">咄&CB03320;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0098b11"/>嚧吽<note place="inline">引<note n="0098034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十三＝十一【甲】</note><app n="0098034"><lem>十三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">十一</rdg></app></note>跋折<note n="0098035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔羅〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0098035"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>跋折<app type="＊" source="0098035"><lem>羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0098036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十三＝十二【三】</note><note n="0098036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十三＝十二【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0098036"><lem>十三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">十二</rdg></app></note>多伽&CB00576;<note place="inline">引</note>也
<lb n="0098b12"/><note n="0098037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以下此真言中甲本無記數</note><note n="0098037" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>以下此真言中甲本無記數</note><note place="inline">十四</note>多伽&CB00576;<note place="inline">引</note>也<note place="inline">十五</note>娑發吒<note place="inline">二合十六</note>娑發吒<note place="inline">二合十七</note>
<lb n="0098b13"/>吽發吒<note place="inline"><note n="0098038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引二合＝二合引【甲】</note><app n="0098038"><lem>引二合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">二合引</rdg></app>十八</note></p>
<lb n="0098b14"/><p>爾時<note n="0098039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＝金剛藥叉王&M062403;【原】【乙】</note><app n="0098039"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】【乙】">金剛藥叉王</rdg></app>說此真言。三千大千世界六種震動。
<lb n="0098b15"/>摩醯首羅等<note n="0098040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝天【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098040"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">天</rdg></app>自在力王眾所居宮殿。皆悉
<lb n="0098b16"/>散動不得安<note n="0098041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穩＝隱【甲】</note><app n="0098041"><lem>穩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">隱</rdg></app>。悉雲集來頂戴藥叉金剛。唯
<lb n="0098b17"/>願大力尊哀愍。令得我無畏安樂威德。藥叉
<lb n="0098b18"/>王白佛言。此等魔王等。所憂惱如何願何為。
<lb n="0098b19"/>佛言猶暫<note n="0098042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝今【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098042"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">今</rdg></app>可愍此等得<note n="0098043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（安）＋樂【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098043"><lem>樂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">安樂</rdg></app>。即許此等已。
<lb n="0098b20"/>即時魔<note n="0098044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＋（等）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098044"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">王等</rdg></app>白忿怒王言。我俱共加神力守護
<lb n="0098b21"/>佛法各退散。若有惡人怨結於善人起<note n="0098045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">擾惱＝惱擾【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098045"><lem>擾惱</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">惱擾</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0098b22"/>法師應當畫神驗忿怒王像隨<note n="0098046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝心【乙】</note><app n="0098046"><lem>意</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">心</rdg></app>大<note n="0098047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">少＝小【乙】</note><app n="0098047"><lem>少</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">小</rdg></app>。作
<lb n="0098b23"/>三角壇向<note n="0098048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（惡）＋人【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098048"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">惡人</rdg></app>所居方。作惡心誦上大靈驗真
<lb n="0098b24"/>言。每日三時二十一遍。滿三日已。惡人死亡
<lb n="0098b25"/>眷屬無殘留。若欲<note n="0098049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（令）＋甦【甲】</note><app n="0098049"><lem>甦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">令甦</rdg></app>生取蓮花根擣末。以大
<lb n="0098b26"/>悲三昧真言一日一夜不飲食。滿一百八遍。
<lb n="0098b27"/>即惡人及眷屬甦。於佛法起歸敬。二羽合拳
<lb n="0098b28"/>屈進力。作<note n="0098050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">谷＝各&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0098050"><lem>谷</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">各</rdg></app>口撥之。心起<note n="0098051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＋（慈）【乙】</note><app n="0098051"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">大慈</rdg></app>悲。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0098b29"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三曼多沒馱<app type="＊" source="0098023"><lem>南</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">喃</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>伽<note n="0098052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03494;婆＝尾波【甲】，比波【乙】</note><note n="0098052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03494;婆＝尾波【甲】，＝比波【乙】</note><app n="0098052"><lem>&CB03494;婆</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">尾波</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">比波</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>設咄
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1220.0098c" n="0098c"/>
<lb n="0098c01"/>嚧嗚&CB00292;<note place="inline">引平</note>莎&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0098053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引）細註【甲】</note><app n="0098053"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0098c02"/><p>欲得佛法大靈驗。先像前作四肘方壇。壇中
<lb n="0098c03"/>安白銅大器。盛滿香水。從月一日迄十五日。
<lb n="0098c04"/>燒香散花致<note n="0098054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔誠〕－【甲】</note><app n="0098054"><lem>誠</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>禮敬。誦大靈驗真言。晝夜無
<lb n="0098c05"/>間不嘗睡眠。全堅固精進。且不<note n="0098055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">安居不安立＝居不立【甲】，居安不立【乙】</note><note n="0098055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">安居不安立＝居不立【甲】，＝居安不立【乙】</note><app n="0098055"><lem>安居不安立</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">居不立</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">居安不立</rdg></app>
<lb n="0098c06"/>留。十五日間無斷絕。<note n="0098056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔而〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098056"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>滿十萬遍。藥<note n="0098057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">叉＋（藥叉）【甲】</note><app n="0098057"><lem>叉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">叉藥叉</rdg></app>王
<lb n="0098c07"/>自現身加持持誦者。即念憐愍有情故。示現
<lb n="0098c08"/>妙形像。二世菩提何非成<note n="0098058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔就〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098058"><lem>就</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。即隨喜怖畏
<lb n="0098c09"/>被此忿怒尊加持。時設諸惡人惡魔惡禽獸。
<lb n="0098c10"/>乃至厭<note n="0098059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禱＝魅【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098059"><lem>禱</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">魅</rdg></app>蠱術魑魅魍魎惡鬼神等。起惡心
<lb n="0098c11"/>欲惱害行人。遠近來向行人住處。則路中自
<lb n="0098c12"/>所殺害。此神驗卅里外圍繞。令無諸障礙。又
<lb n="0098c13"/>金剛藥叉為施調伏故。說大威怒王根本大
<lb n="0098c14"/>心真<note n="0098060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（曰）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098060"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">言曰</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0098061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自是&CB00057;至儀軌十一字甲本作本文</note><note n="0098061" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>自是&CB00057;至儀軌十一字甲本作本文</note>是&CB00057;印甚祕密故。非表儀軌。即在別卷。親近阿闍梨。承事可習學。甚<note n="0098062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">密故＝深故【甲】，祕密也【乙】</note><note n="0098062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">密故＝深故【甲】，＝祕密也【乙】</note><app n="0098062"><lem>密故</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">深故</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">祕密也</rdg></app></note>誦
<lb n="0098c15"/>此&CB00057;時。一切魔王鬼眾。<note n="0098063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不得＝得不&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0098063"><lem>不得</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">得不</rdg></app>安穩怖懼之事。
<lb n="0098c16"/>如大靈驗真言無異。<note n="0098064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00057;印＝&CB00057;印有&M062403;【原】，但印&CB00057;在【甲】，但印&CB00057;【乙】</note><note n="0098064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00057;印＝&CB00057;印有&M062403;【原】，＝但印&CB00057;在【甲】，＝但印&CB00057;【乙】</note><app n="0098064"><lem>&CB00057;印</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&CB00057;印有</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">但印&CB00057;在</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">但印&CB00057;</rdg></app>別。若欲行此&CB00057;。如
<lb n="0098c17"/>聖不動尊念誦儀軌。而作法先右膝著地。至
<lb n="0098c18"/>心歸<note n="0098065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝依【甲】</note><app n="0098065"><lem>命</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">依</rdg></app>一切佛菩薩。懺悔無始生死罪障。隨
<lb n="0098c19"/>喜一切諸佛菩薩所集善根。勸請一切如來
<lb n="0098c20"/>聖眾。發菩提心供養諸佛即勸請真言曰</p>
<lb n="0098c21"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00085;日<note n="0098066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0098066"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>藥叉<note place="inline">二合</note>也多多那伽梨那
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1220.0099a" n="0099a"/>
<lb n="0099a01"/><note place="inline">二</note><note n="0099001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尾＋（蘇）【乙】</note><app n="0099001"><lem>尾</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">尾蘇</rdg></app>&CB03265;<note n="0099002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吒＝&CB00062;【甲】</note><app n="0099002"><lem>吒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00062;</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>吽吽<note n="0099003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎＝娑【甲】</note><app n="0099003"><lem>莎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">娑</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0099a02"/><p>澡像真言曰</p>
<lb n="0099a03"/><p type="dharani">唵吽娑婆嚕&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>唅</p>
<lb n="0099a04"/><p>閼伽真言曰</p>
<lb n="0099a05"/><p type="dharani">唵阿頗羅<note place="inline">二合</note>底&CB00576;<note place="inline">引</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0099a06"/><note n="0099004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本自奉座至一切七百四十九字缺之</note><note n="0099004" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>〔奉座…一切〕七百四十<corr sic="九" resp="CBETA.say">八</corr>字－【甲】</note><p>奉座真言曰</p>
<lb n="0099a07"/><p type="dharani">唵尾迦尼左羅尼<note place="inline">二</note>噁<note place="inline">入</note></p>
<lb n="0099a08"/><p>著衣瓔珞真言曰</p>
<lb n="0099a09"/><p type="dharani">唵矩尼矩尼薩矩尼<note place="inline">引</note>也伊<note place="inline"><note n="0099005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">牟＝平入【乙】</note><app n="0099005"><lem>牟</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">平入</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0099a10"/><p>獻香花燈塗真言曰</p>
<lb n="0099a11"/><p type="dharani">唵摩尼<note place="inline">引</note>娜伽伽娜三摩三摩<note n="0099006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矩＝舍【乙】</note><app n="0099006"><lem>矩</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">舍</rdg></app>&CB03306;提噁莎
<lb n="0099a12"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0099a13"/><p>讚嘆藥叉金剛曰</p>
<lb n="0099a14"/><p type="dharani">&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>噯咄羅藥乞叉&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底哩&CB00576;
<lb n="0099a15"/>尾&CB03265;梨<note place="inline">二合</note>賀&CB00576;<note place="inline">引上</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>摩訶藥乞叉
<lb n="0099a16"/><note place="inline">上</note>藥乞叉<note place="inline">上</note>婆&CB00576;伽&CB00576;也<note place="inline">引平</note>噁<note place="inline">短</note></p>
<lb n="0099a17"/><p>生歡喜悅意。可誦此讚嘆偈</p>
<lb n="0099a18"/><lg><l>善哉善哉噁藥叉</l><l>憐愍有情我等類</l>
<lb n="0099a19"/><l>無倫比像化含靈</l><l>何者寧為<note n="0099007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">何＝伺【乙】</note><app n="0099007"><lem>何</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">伺</rdg></app>惱法</l></lg>
<lb n="0099a20"/><p>加持數珠真言曰</p>
<lb n="0099a21"/><p type="dharani">唵縛日囉豎尼</p>
<lb n="0099a22"/><p>奉送真言曰</p>
<lb n="0099a23"/><p type="dharani">唵尾訖<note n="0099008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">灑＝麗&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0099008" corr="麗" resp="【原】">灑</sic><note place="inline">二合</note>耶吽噁<note place="inline">入</note></p>
<lb n="0099a24"/><p>上所說十種供養讚嘆等真言。皆持用三股
<lb n="0099a25"/>金剛杵。二羽中受鈷當心誦一一真言。各應
<lb n="0099a26"/>想流出威德。執持金剛鈷。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0099a27"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>參&CB01511;縛日羅<note place="inline">二合</note>醯&CB00576;尾吠縛日羅<note place="inline">二合</note>噁</p>
<lb n="0099a28"/><p>若欲一切障難解脫。合丸藥二兩。各把左右
<lb n="0099a29"/>掌。踞著者而誦大靈驗真言七遍。加持著者
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1220.0099b" n="0099b"/>
<lb n="0099b01"/>塗背後。一時解脫一切障難一切口舌橫死
<lb n="0099b02"/>短命等。若又欲急殺惡人。<note n="0099009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畫人＝書彼人【乙】</note><app n="0099009"><lem>畫人</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">書彼人</rdg></app>像姓名置調
<lb n="0099b03"/>伏壇。最初角削竹釘穿立腹<note n="0099010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中＋（調）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0099010"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">中調</rdg></app>。誦大靈驗真
<lb n="0099b04"/>言。以<note n="0099011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚗噁＝暴惡【乙】</note><app n="0099011"><lem>嚗噁</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">暴惡</rdg></app>卒怒心。<note n="0099012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00057;＝加持&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0099012" corr="加持" resp="【原】">&CB00057;</sic>一百八遍。一遍一
<lb n="0099b05"/><note n="0099013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">打＋（人像）【乙】</note><app n="0099013"><lem>打</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">打人像</rdg></app>便<note n="0099014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斃＝卒死【乙】</note><app n="0099014"><lem>斃</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">卒死</rdg></app>。又欲急縛惡人令歸佛道。以惡心
<lb n="0099b06"/>誦大&CB00057;三遍。取黑石共後發吒。羽內迴之自
<lb n="0099b07"/>然被縛。又欲<note n="0099015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">解免＝解脫此&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0099015"><lem>解免</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">解脫此</rdg></app>者。誦大慈三昧<note n="0099016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明＝真言【乙】</note><app n="0099016"><lem>明</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">真言</rdg></app>三遍。
<lb n="0099b08"/>便得本心即言。自今已後歸依佛道。更不<note n="0099017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔生〕－【乙】</note><app n="0099017"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0099b09"/>起邪<note n="0099018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＋（&CB00308;惡）【乙】</note><app n="0099018"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">見&CB00308;惡</rdg></app>不善心。又欲好女自得及令他得。松
<lb n="0099b10"/><note n="0099019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皮＝葉【乙】</note><app n="0099019"><lem>皮</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">葉</rdg></app>書好女姓名。繫像前誦大慈三昧真言。七
<lb n="0099b11"/>遍啟白威怒王。如是每日三時繫念。<note n="0099020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白啟＝迫啟白【乙】</note><app n="0099020"><lem>白啟</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">迫啟白</rdg></app>威
<lb n="0099b12"/>怒王慈愍故。自乘好女<note n="0099021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意不＝心非【乙】</note><app n="0099021"><lem>意。不</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">心非</rdg></app>令生他心自從
<lb n="0099b13"/>宮宅出<note n="0099022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00564;來＝來極【乙】</note><app n="0099022"><lem>&CB00564;來</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">來極</rdg></app>。愛著夫人。更無他念。寧他妻
<lb n="0099b14"/><note n="0099023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">非＝不【乙】</note><app n="0099023"><lem>非</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">不</rdg></app>他<note n="0099024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夫＝妻【乙】</note><app n="0099024"><lem>夫</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">妻</rdg></app>。夫厭妻妻厭夫。一心一向歸後夫
<lb n="0099b15"/>婦妻。<note n="0099025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔俱〕－【乙】</note><app n="0099025"><lem>俱</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>常發菩提心。&M010527;教化夫<note n="0099026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人矣〕－【乙】</note><app n="0099026"><lem>人矣</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。又欲
<lb n="0099b16"/>得官位。像前至心燒香。設種種供養。三日三
<lb n="0099b17"/>夜乃至七日七夜間。可誦大慈三昧。<note n="0099027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">真言＝&CB00057;【乙】</note><app n="0099027"><lem>真言</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00057;</rdg></app>祈
<lb n="0099b18"/>願。所願無一不成。<note n="0099028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔則作…就〕八字－【乙】</note><app n="0099028" word-count="8"><lem>則作增益法。自成就</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>唯
<lb n="0099b19"/><note n="0099029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">修行＝作&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0099029"><lem>修行</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">作</rdg></app>法時。隨念向望方。細示方如護摩壇作
<lb n="0099b20"/>法已。欲出道場誦此真言。發遣聖眾。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0099b21"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>藥乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>底那底他也<note place="inline">二合</note>毘
<lb n="0099b22"/>吽吽噁</p>
<lb n="0099b23"/><p>說此等種<note n="0099030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雜＝種【乙】</note><app n="0099030"><lem>雜</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">種</rdg></app>威德瞋<note n="0099031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怒＋（王）【乙】</note><app n="0099031"><lem>怒</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">怒王</rdg></app>法時。一切魔怨調
<lb n="0099b24"/>伏加衛護。願護持佛法。是故行者修習時。慎
<lb n="0099b25"/><note n="0099032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莫起惡＝勿不善&M062403;【原】，勿起惡【乙】</note><note n="0099032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莫起惡＝勿不善&M062403;【原】，＝勿起惡【乙】</note><app n="0099032"><lem>莫起惡</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">勿不善</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">勿起惡</rdg></app>心數<note n="0099033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（自損）＋損【乙】</note><app n="0099033"><lem>損</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">自損損</rdg></app>他。有智人善悟是祕道。輒
<lb n="0099b26"/>亂不得誦&CB00057;。唯除<note n="0099034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耎＝柔【乙】</note><app n="0099034"><lem>耎</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">柔</rdg></app>和忍辱<note n="0099035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＝者【乙】</note><app n="0099035"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app>。年滿四十
<lb n="0099b27"/><note n="0099036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而得自順順他＝未年滿足者得自損損他【乙】</note><app n="0099036"><lem>而得自順順他</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">未年滿足者得自損損他</rdg></app>。智者若幼稚人行好習誦時
<lb n="0099b28"/>不得解脫道。<note n="0099037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">隨＝墮落【乙】</note><app n="0099037"><lem>隨</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">墮落</rdg></app>自損損他深<note n="0099038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＝咎&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0099038"><lem>過</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">咎</rdg></app>。行者多應
<lb n="0099b29"/>有慈<note n="0099039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悲＝愍【三】</note><note n="0099039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悲＝愍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0099039"><lem>悲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">愍</rdg></app>利益一切有情界。出堂任意<note n="0099040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔而〕－【乙】</note><app n="0099040"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>轉
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1220.0099c" n="0099c"/>
<lb n="0099c01"/>讀大乘。<note n="0099041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（必）＋住【乙】</note><app n="0099041"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">必住</rdg></app>不退轉地</p>
<lb n="0099c02"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>金剛藥<note n="0099042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">叉＋（瞋怒息災大威神驗）【甲】</note><app n="0099042"><lem>叉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">叉瞋怒息災大威神驗</rdg></app>念誦儀軌<note n="0099043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本奧書曰寬治四年三月二十一日於仁和寺喜多院酉時許書寫畢，嘉保二年四月十七日於高野奧院東菴室大僧都奉受了</note></jhead></juan></div1>
